dcterms:description: The Nitrogen oxides (NO) concentration dataset recorded from Stockholm city monitors air pollution parameters to provide air quality surveillance. It includes measurements from three stations over a period of time.

dcterms:description: The Ozone concentration dataset reflects the strength of fossil fuel usage and its emissions, collected from three stations in Stockholm city over a period of time.

dcterms:description: The PM10 concentration dataset includes measurements of particulate matter with a diameter of less than 10 micrometers, collected from three stations in Stockholm city over a period of time.
